JOINS SSW FORK DONE EARLIER AND CHANGED THE LOWER SECTION OF ROUTE. HAS A 440' WALL THAT WE BROKE INTO TWO 220' RAPPELS. NOTE PHOTO SHOWS THIS 440' DROP IN THE LOWER PORTION OF THE CANYON - ANOTHER VERY BIG DROP SECTION ABOVE ALSO
